+
+
+
+## Example Usage
+
+```terraform
+data "cloudflare_notification_policy" "example_notification_policy" {
+  account_id = "023e105f4ecef8ad9ca31a8372d0c353"
+  policy_id = "0da2b59e-f118-439d-8097-bdfb215203c9"
+}
+```
